data.description: This beautiful ranch style home has 3 bedrooms 2 full bath. Walking into this well kept home, you have two nice size bedroom to the right of the home, the family room is very spacious with vaulted ceiling. Eat-in kitchen. The spacious master bedroom has a tub and shower combo, with walk in closet. this home has so many upgrades. New roof, new HVAC, new custom sliding door, new dishwasher and water heater. Outdoors you have a huge backyard for entertainment. The neighborhood offer so many amenities. Walking trails, pools, clubhouse and play area for the kids, so much more. your minutes away to local shops, restaurants, downtown and Beaches. If square footage matter please measure. Listing agent is not responsible for any inaccurate information that may be incorrect.
